info: Victoria's Secret & Co. operates as a specialty retailer of women's intimate, personal care, and beauty products worldwide. The company offers bras, panties, lingerie, casual sleepwear and athleisure, loungewear, swimwear, and activewear, as well as fragrances and body care products, and accessories under the Victoria's Secret and PINK brands. It operates approximately 1,400 retail stores. The company is headquartered in Reynoldsburg, Ohio.
